{"tid":1550830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone可以係唔解鎖下證明電話係自己同打律師電話方法","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T15:55:42.000Z","uid":275475,"like":70,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"ac41cfe7b17ce035754680dbb1585d68bb27f272","tid":1550830,"uid":275475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:58:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n教大家一個iphone都可以不解鎖下證明電話係自己方法：<br />\n記住取消face id touch id！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nset好以下步驟後按五下power鍵啟動<br />\n<br />\n1.set醫療檔案 （medical ID）填自己全名<br />\n 仲可以填法律支援電話，不解鎖也可以打電話找律師<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OjBjXQ6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOjBjXQ6.png&h=e9c96d19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nsearch sos<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LdfMCRc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLdfMCRc.png&h=20db85d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.emergency contact填義務律師 or自己律師 家人 可信任朋友 電話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PLfdhRk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPLfdhRk.png&h=1c68e2c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n實戰篇<br />\n3.<br />\n按五下power鍵啟動<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9KHORc0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9KHORc0.png&h=59fabd74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1有真名 2自己大頭相 3出生年月日 <br />\n你完全無理由質疑啦掛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n病歷如果你真係有高血壓 糖尿 哮喘記得填！<br />\n不幸被捕被屈可以要求提供適切醫療協助<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TdYnbgE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTdYnbgE.png&h=f7d36182&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外lock screen 情況下向左撥就可以開相機<br />\n相信99%都知道<br />\n但緊急情況可能會忘記<br />\n記住有權拍片保障自己"},{"pid":"b7b04fcc6b3b77a0d5f3fa56ce3612ce269c83d2","tid":1550830,"uid":160247,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:58:49.000Z","msg":"試下中英都跟住唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》 Glory be to thee, Hong Kong<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流 In angst, tears are shed o&rsquo;er this Land<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨 With rage, fears are crushed, in arms we stand<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透 We rise, undefiled, our voice shall never die<br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡 As we yearn, our freedom nighs<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走 With eyes blinded, long it comes the night<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後 In faith, banners high, we pledge to fight<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透 Our flesh, sacrificed, our blood shall write this song<br />\n建自由 光輝 香港 Free this Land, &ldquo;Stand with Hong Kong!&rdquo;<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜 Stars will fall, and darkness fills the air<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲 Storms will break, bedazzled by our gallant flares!<br />\n捍自由 We shall strike<br />\n來齊集這裡 This perilous night<br />\n來全力抗對 Determined to fight<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅&quot; With hope, with song, with dignity!<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港 Glory enshrined, break our chains! Hold our lines!<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命 Freedom shall rise! Revolution of our Time!<br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽 Liberty thrives, rights divine, in our unending strides<br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港 Glory be to thee, Hong Kong!"},{"pid":"f576c2410dfafc1401495ca7efb91bff72cbae39","tid":1550830,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:58:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1bcf664800bcf9b9912d81dfeea4c11ebf28eb0d","tid":1550830,"uid":181035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:41:35.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"77d29a3e72dbf6a1d512342ab7b81ec7ada3ea66","tid":1550830,"uid":3764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:42:33.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"f1e9c72f5978b4251c22706378952ff411c62c0b","tid":1550830,"uid":275475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1bcf664800bcf9b9912d81dfeea4c11ebf28eb0d","tid":1550830,"uid":181035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:41:35.000Z","msg":"再推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:43:35.000Z","msg":"多謝曬！！<br />\nP牌感謝你"},{"pid":"4878ae3dd02b8fc1075849d243dd61361da4723f","tid":1550830,"uid":47999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:44:06.000Z","msg":"IOS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd78be582e10df83b4ff509a26ea85ba689b80b","tid":1550830,"uid":133380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:45:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e459f75ccbed9b01d83f827558ea3cf25298ea4","tid":1550830,"uid":229910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:46:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02b77f9995585d7907251a490bc810a4e8ebbeab","tid":1550830,"uid":122282,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:48:26.000Z","msg":"試左 Android都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32253186b26870a0eec513da5f8abb19d7a89e6","tid":1550830,"uid":232167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:48:37.000Z","msg":"熱門一個908嘅post都冇？入嚟